snippet.textDisplay: My husband made me a beautiful gift by introducing me to this song which I would call "prayer in music". He is abroad now and I listen to it every day and these verses cancel the distance that separates us. May Allah reunite our family soon🤲🏻 and may each of you reading this post live in love and serenity with your loved ones. May Allah place His loving gaze on us all. I❤U Usman, my beloved husband.
